{"word":"τρώκτης","slug":"τρώκτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n105801\" key=\"trw/kths\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τρώκ-της</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ου</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">τρώγω</etym>) <sense id=\"n105801.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">gnawer, nibbler</tr_>: but in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:289\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.289</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:416\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.416</biblScope></bibl>, Phoenician traffickers are called <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρῶκται,</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">greedy knaves</tr_>; so <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τ. σφόδρ᾽ ἐστίν</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Com.Adesp.\">Com.Adesp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">606</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; and Gramm. explain <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρώκτης</foreign> by <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φάγος, φιλοκερδής, πανοῦργος, ἀπατεών,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phot.</author></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1757:51\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1757.51</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φιλοχρήματοι καὶ τ.</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philostr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Her.Prooem.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n105801.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρῶκται χεῖρες</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">greedy</tr_> hands, of a usurer, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.409</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Antiphan.</author></bibl>, dub. cj.). </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n105801.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a sea-fish with sharp teeth,</tr_> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἀμία</ref> </xr> (q.v.), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:1:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ NA\">NA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.5</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}